item.title: Welcome to my online portfolio!
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Hey! I'm Anekha Ajith, 3rd Year Creative Digital Media student

at the Institute of Technology Blanchardstown.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Hey, Anekha here! I am a3rd Year Creative Digital Media student in the Institute of Technology Blanchardstown, Dublin. I am a very creative and outgoing person, I love meeting new people and taking on new opportunities. I particularly enjoy photography, graphic design and filmmaking within the broad spectrum of modules in the course. My interests include fashion designing and dance outside of college.

I am currently seeking an internship to apply my experience assisting a company’s service to their clients using my skills in Digital Media.

This is a rough cut of a documentary that was done as part of a group project. We interviewed Michael Slavin, and author who runs a book shop at The Hill of Tara. He is visited daily by the people that come to Tara.
[embed]https://vimeo.com/148521683[/embed]
A short video portraying friendship, created for a Digital Video Techniques project.
